{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About - Company Research Platform{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-center mb-5">About Company Research Platform</h1>

    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <p class="lead">
                The Company Research Platform is an AI-powered solution for gathering comprehensive
                business intelligence on companies across various industries. Built with Symfony
                and Neuron AI, this platform provides research capabilities traditionally available
                only to financial analysts and investment professionals.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Company Research Made Easy</h2>
            <p>
                Our platform simplifies the process of researching companies by leveraging
                artificial intelligence to gather, analyze, and generate insights about:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Company overviews and basic information</li>
                <li>Financial data from quarterly and annual reports</li>
                <li>Leadership profiles and executive backgrounds</li>
                <li>Competitive landscape and market positioning</li>
                <li>Investment highlights and risk factors</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Whether you're an investor, analyst, business development professional, or
                simply curious about a company, our platform provides the information you need
                in an easy-to-understand format.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Powered by Advanced Technology</h2>
            <p>
                The platform is built on a modern technology stack, combining the reliability
                of Symfony PHP framework with the power of AI through Neuron AI integration:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Symfony Framework</strong>: Provides a robust, scalable foundation</li>
                <li><strong>Neuron AI</strong>: Delivers intelligent insights and analysis</li>
                <li><strong>Cloud Foundry</strong>: Ensures reliable, scalable hosting</li>
                <li><strong>Modern Frontend</strong>: Responsive design for all devices</li>
                <li><strong>PDF/Excel Export</strong>: Generate shareable reports</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                The platform is deployed on Tanzu Platform for Cloud Foundry, ensuring
                enterprise-grade reliability and security.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <div class="card bg-light">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Disclaimer</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This platform is intended for demonstration purposes only. The information
                        generated by the AI system should not be considered financial advice.
                        Always verify information with official sources before making investment
                        decisions. The platform and its AI capabilities are part of a showcase
                        for Tanzu Platform for Cloud Foundry with the GenAI tile integration.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to get started?</h2>
            <a href="{{ path('company_search') }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mx-2">Search Companies</a>
            <a href="{{ path('company_new') }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg mx-2">Add New Company</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
